
To Create the final Windows files, the following applications are required:

	* ANT (http://ant.apache.org)
	* 7-Zip (http://www.7-zip.org)
	* Izpack (http://www.izforge.com/izpack/)
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* You must install 7-Zip(http://www.7-zip.org) on the PC to enable the setup.exe creation

* 7-Zip directory must be in the PATH System Environment Variable

* Before the final setup can be created, please copy the Tomcat and Mysql installers into the ext-files directory and modify the ext-files.properties file to set the filenames of the installs.

* The final output files are stored in the target directory
